Class ServerCommandHandler

  • java.lang.Object
    • it.polimi.ingsw.ps19.server.ServerCommandHandler
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    CommandObserver

    public class ServerCommandHandler
extends java.lang.Object
implements CommandObserver
    This class handles every command arriving from Client to Server, calling methods of MatchHandler The reference to Match is needed to get player objects from the match.

    Mirko
